# Google Maps API Key Setup

The Google Maps integration requires a valid API key.

1.  Go to the [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com/).
2.  Enable the **Maps Embed API**.
3.  Create an API key in **APIs & Services > Credentials**.
4.  Add the key as an environment variable in the **Settings** menu of this app:
    ```env
    VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_actual_key_here
    ```
